A '''stuffed bantha''' was a toy for children. Similar toys were the stuffed [[Tauntaun/Legends|tauntaun]]<ref name="Sacrifice">''[[Legacy of the Force: Sacrifice]]''</ref> and the stuffed [[Dewback/Legends|dewback]].<ref name="Star Wars Galaxies">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

==History==
During the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Night Forael Wren]], the daughter of [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Lavina Durada-Vashne Wren]], owned a purple-colored stuffed bantha and she took it with her when she was kidnapped by the [[Thaereian military]].<ref name="Night's Homecoming">{{LivingForce|Night Eyes: Night's Homecoming}}</ref>

[[Vardias Tyne]] made a toy bantha to give to the bantha-worshiping [[Dim-U/Legends|Dim-U]] monks in [[1 ABY/Legends|1 ABY]], as he hoped to appease them, after they hired a [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] called [[Rhalia Jinsari]] to kill him.<ref name="Star Wars Galaxies" />

[[File:Bantha_Traxx_toy.jpg|thumb|left|160px|[[Bantha Traxx]] Boutique gift shop]]
The stuffed bantha was the favorite toy of [[Lumpawaroo/Legends|Lumpawaroo]]. When an Imperial search party invaded Lumpy's house on [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]], a [[Imperial Navy Trooper/Legends|naval guard]] ripped the head off the toy bantha. This made Lumpy very upset, and motivated him to create a signal that would fool the Imperials into leaving his house and going back to their base.<ref name="The Star Wars Holiday Special">''[[The Star Wars Holiday Special]]''</ref>

Stuffed banthas were also sold in the [[Bantha Traxx]] Boutique gift shop on [[Lianna/Legends|Lianna]].<ref name="wh">''[[Wretched Hives of Scum & Villainy]]''</ref>

In [[8 ABY/Legends|8.5 ABY]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] found a stuffed bantha belonging to the daughter of [[Kitster Chanchani Banai]]. It was a sign to her that [[Tamora Spice]] was being evasive about being alone in the house.<ref name="Tatooine Ghost">''[[Tatooine Ghost]]''</ref>

In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] would give his daughter, [[Allana Djo Solo|Allana]], a stuffed bantha<ref name="Legacy of the Force: Tempest">''[[Legacy of the Force: Tempest]]''</ref> and later a stuffed tauntaun<ref name="Sacrifice" /> as a present. She named the tauntaun "Jacen" after him, so that when he was away and she missed him, she could talk to the tauntaun.

